WORK SUMMARY :
Assignment was given to developed a Dynamic List Application using React.js that allows users to manage a list of tasks interactively.
Implemented add and delete functionality using the use State hook to store and update tasks dynamically.
Used form input fields and event handling to capture user input and add new tasks to the list.


LEARNING OUTCOMES :
Learned how to manage dynamic data using React Hooks (use State) in functional components.
Gained understanding of handling user events such as form submission and button clicks in React.
